title: SupDucks Acquisition
body:
The following is a proposal for BeetsDAO to acquire up to 5 ETH worth of SupDucks while the project is still at a very early stage. This project went under the radar of most of the NFT space. It launched at midnight EST on Friday so we are only on the third day the project has been live. Here are the reasons to consider this investment. 
1.	The artist creator frankynines is an OG in the crypto community having worked at Dapper Labs and has been developing the SupDucks concept for a few years (early SupDuck works are on the blockchain from 2019). He even designed the Nyan blunts in our recent promotion with Snoop. Here is information on frankynines https://www.frankyaguilar.com/ and here are three tweets or retweets from Snoop referencing frankynines or the SupDuck project just from this weekend alone.  https://twitter.com/RealSupDucks/status/1416780266950074379?s=20
https://twitter.com/SnoopDogg/status/1416785372189581313?s=20
https://twitter.com/SnoopDogg/status/1416645382658953224?s=20
2.	Here is a very distinct roadmap for SupDucks that was just published early this morning: https://www.notion.so/Roadmap-c4cd1eebdd1a4382ad845e2134b5f556
3.	This project has a well-designed smart contract, for example the Ducks are all generated on chain. 
4.	The artwork is very well done and stands out in a sea of NFTs. The colors pop and there is a lot of humor in the work. Some notables like Bryan Brinkman already showcase a SupDuck in their pfp, here is Dan from OpenSea singing frankynines praises: https://twitter.com/dan_OpenSea/status/1416831817810907143?s=20
5.	There has already been a lot of price action in this project. Faze Banks a professional video gamer with 2.7M twitter followers traded a CryptoPunk for a SupDuck on Saturday. There have been 8 sales at 20 ETH or greater already including two 50 ETH sales. SupDucks is a top five project as of this writing over a seven-day average with less than 3 days of sales. 

Voting for this proposal authorizes BeetsDAO treasury to spend up to 5 ETH for the acquisition of several SupDucks, focusing on the floor Ducks. This is a chance to accumulate a portfolio of a project that has the potential to be as large as BAYC if not larger. The plan would be to hold the SupDucks until the floor was sufficiently high before considering any sales. Given we did not acquire the Bun B we only need to transfer 2 ETH of the 5 ETH requested to the trading wallet. Note this is a timely vote since the SupDucks floor is rising. Please vote even if you decide to vote no. Thank you for your participation.
